<FIRST>r i AM-Poland-Solidarity     06-22 0568</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Poland-Solidarity,0586</SECOND>
<HEAD>Solidarity Citizens Committee To Focus on Building Union</HEAD>
<HEAD>EDS: RETRANMITTING a0803 to fix slug to distinguish from a0704, AM-Poland</HEAD>
<BYLINE>By DEBORAH G. SEWARD</BYLINE>
<BYLINE>Associated Press Writer</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>WARSAW, Poland (AP) </DATELINE>
