<FIRST>a a AM-ReligionRoundupAdv23-1stLd-Writethru b0366   06-22 0614</FIRST>
<SECOND>AM-Religion Roundup Adv 23-1st Ld-Writethru, b0366,0633</SECOND>
<HEAD>$Adv23</HEAD>
<HEAD>For Release Fri AMs, June 23 and Thereafter</HEAD>
<HEAD>Eds: In third item, DAYTON .. CORRECT spelling of Committee in b0366
of June 21.</HEAD>
<DATELINE>SAN ANTONIO (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
