<HEAD>$100 Millon Satellite Contract Goes to GE Plant in New Jersey</HEAD>
<DATELINE>WASHINGTON (AP) </DATELINE>
<TEXT>
   The U.S. Air Force has awarded a nearly $100
million contract to General Electric Co. for production of 26 global
